<div class="landing-container">
  <%= render 'shared/navbar' %>
  <section id="section1" class="image-bg">
    <div class="background-picture">
      <div class="ww-home-text d-flex justify-content-center align-items-center flex-column">
        <h1 class="wanstead-wags-title wanstead-wags text-center">Wanstead Wags</h1>
        <h1 class="ww-home-services font text-center">PROFESSIONAL DOG WALKING SERVICES</h1>
        <%= link_to("BOOK TODAY", new_contact_form_path, class: "text-center button mt-5") %>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="section2" class="color-bg" style="background-color: #011712;">
    <div class="green-background welcome-section">
      <div class="welcome-message">
        <h1 class="welcome wanstead-wags-title titles" style="color: #40FFB5;">Welcome to<br>Wanstead Wags</h1>
        <p class="text padding-text">At Wanstead Wags, we provide care for dogs with different needs, ensuring they have fulfilling walks in nature that balance physical exercise and mental stimulation.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="welcome-to-photo">
        <%= image_tag "dogs_walking_forrests.png", alt: "Photo of a dog walking in the woods", class: "photo-two" %>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="section3" class="color-bg" style="background-color: #F4CEE2;">
    <div class="prices-div">
      <div class="d-flex justify-content-center flex-column align-items-center">
        <h1 class="wanstead-wags-title titles prices" style="color: #032B22;">Services</h1>
        <p class="price-list" style="font-family: Lato, serif, sans-serif !important;">Click here to see our full price list.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="services">
        <div class="d-flex align-items-center services-flex">
          <div class="service-image-flex">
            <%= image_tag "solo_walks.png", alt: "Photo of a dog walking in the woods on their own", class: "services-images" %>
          </div>
          <div class="d-flex flex-column align-items-center services-paragraph">
            <h1 class="text services-description service-name">Solo Dog Walks</h1>
            <p class="text services-description services-font services-text">One-on-one adventures for your pup in nature – peaceful walks in the woods, fields, and lakes for gentle exercise and mental stimulation.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="d-flex align-items-center services-flex">
          <div class="service-image-flex">
            <%= image_tag "group_walks.png", alt: "Photo of a 5 dogs in a field on leashes with a walker", class: "services-images" %>
          </div>
          <div class="d-flex flex-column align-items-center services-paragraph">
            <h1 class="text services-description service-name">Group Dog Walks</h1>
            <p class="text services-description services-font services-text">Fun, social walks with 3-4 other friendly dogs! Let your dog make new friends while exploring parks, fields, and woodlands.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="d-flex align-items-center services-flex">
          <div class="service-image-flex">
            <%= image_tag "pet_sitting.png", alt: "Photo of a dog sitting on the living room floor", class: "services-images" %>
          </div>
          <div class="d-flex flex-column align-items-center services-paragraph">
            <h1 class="text services-description service-name">Run & Stimulate Package</h1>
            <p class="text services-description services-font services-text">A 45-minute run (6-8km) plus 30 minutes of brain games and training to burn off energy and keep your dog sharp and happy.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="section4" class="color-bg" style="background-color: #EFEDE7;">
    <div class="how-to-book">
      <div class="booking-instructions d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center">
        <div class="steps d-flex flex-column">
          <h1 class="wanstead-wags-title titles prices booking-title" style="color: #032B22; margin: 0;">How To Book</h1>
          <p class="green-text color">Booking a walk with me is quick and easy! Simply follow these steps:</p>
          <ol>
            <li class="green-text indent">Contact Me: Use the contact form on this website or send me an email to let me know your dog’s needs.</li>
            <li class="green-text indent">Schedule a Meet-and-Greet: I’ll arrange a time to meet you and your pup! This helps me understand their personality, walking style, and any special instructions you might have.</li>
            <li class="green-text indent">Choose Your Service: Select the type of walk you need—individual, group, and your preferred days and times.</li>
            <li class="green-text indent">Confirm the Booking: I’ll confirm your booking and provide a simple payment process to secure your slot.</li>
          </ol>
            <p class="green-text">That’s it! I’ll handle the rest, ensuring your dog has a safe, fun, and energising walk while you focus on your day.</p>
          <div class="d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center mt-4">
            <h3 class="wanstead-wags-title booking-title" style="font-size: 2rem; color: #032B22;">Ready to book?</h3>
            <a href="/"><p class="text-center button" style="margin:0;">BOOK TODAY</p></a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="d-flex flex-column doggy-picture align-items-center">
          <%= image_tag "how-to-book-image.png", alt: "Photo of a dog walking in the woods", class: "photo-three" %>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="section5" class="color-bg" style="background-color: #011712;">
    <div class="blog-background">
      <h1 class="welcome wanstead-wags-title titles d-flex justify-content-center" style="color: #40FFB5;">Blogs About Dogs</h1>
      <div class="blog-posts container mt-4">
        <div class="row">
          <% @posts.each_with_index do |post, index| %>
            <% if index < 3 %>
              <div class="col-md-4 mb-4">
                <a href="<%= blogs_post_path(post.fields[:slug]) %>" class="post-link">
                  <div class="d-flex flex-column align-items-center">
                    <% if post.fields[:blog_image].present? %>
                      <% image_url = "https:" + post.fields[:blog_image].url %>
                      <%= image_tag image_url, alt: "Photo of a dog walking in the woods on their own.", class: "blog-images" %>
                    <% else %>
                      <p>No image available</p>
                    <% end %>
                    <div class="post-description">
                      <p class="text blogs-description"><%= post.fields[:title] %></p>
                      <p class="text blog-text text-center"><%= post.fields[:description] %></p>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </a>
              </div>
            <% end %>
          <% end %>
        </div>
      </div>
      <%= link_to("VIEW ALL", blogs_path, class:"view-all-link") %>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="section6" class="color-bg" style="background-color: #EFEDE7;">
    <div class="how-to-book">
      <div class="booking-instructions about-me d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center">
        <div class="d-flex flex-column about-me-photo">
          <%= image_tag "about-me-image.png", alt: "Photo of a dog walking in the woods", class: "about-me-photo" %>
        </div>
        <div class="about-me-text d-flex flex-column">
          <h1 class="wanstead-wags-title titles prices booking-title" style="color: #032B22; margin: 0;">About Me</h1>
          <p class="green-text color"> Hi! I’m Jayden, a passionate dog lover and a local dog walker in Wanstead! I’ve always adored spending time with dogs—whether it’s enjoying their boundless energy, forming special bonds, or simply seeing their tails wag with joy.<br><br>Combining my love for animals and my enthusiasm for staying active, I’ve found dog walking to be the perfect way to do what I love while helping busy pet owners like you. Originally from Marlow, Buckinghamshire, I recently moved to Wanstead whilst I study at university. I bring flexibility, reliability, and a strong work ethic to everything I do—including caring for your pets. You can trust that your dog will be in safe, caring, and responsible hands with me.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</div>
